# Commit Message Template
# Format: [type](scope): emoji title_in_english
#
# Example: [feat](CatUI): ✨ Add CatCardView component
#
# Types:
#   feat:     New feature
#   fix:      Bug fix
#   docs:     Documentation changes
#   style:    Code style changes (formatting, no logic change)
#   refactor: Code refactoring
#   test:     Adding or updating tests
#   chore:    Build process or auxiliary tool changes
#   perf:     Performance improvements
#
# Scopes:
#   CatList    (CatList feature)
#   CatDetail  (CatDetail feature)
#   Voting     (Voting feature)
#   VoteHistory (VoteHistory feature)
#   CatUI      (design system)
#   Core       (shared services/models)
#   Config     (project configuration)
#   Network    (networking layer)
#   Persistence (data persistence)
#
# Emojis:
#   ✨ New feature
#   🐛 Bug fix
#   📚 Documentation
#   🎨 UI/Style
#   ♻️  Refactor
#   ✅ Tests
#   🔧 Config/Chore
#   ⚡️ Performance
#   🚀 Release
#   🎉 Initial commit
#
# [type](scope): emoji title_in_english
#
# Detailed description of changes:
# - What changed
# - Why it changed
# - Any breaking changes or important notes
